{"prompt": "Generate a website for a podcasting network. The website should be dynamic and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>EchoSphere Network</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #ff4500; /* OrangeRed */\n            --secondary-color: #ff7f50; /* Coral */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #1a1a1a;\n            --footer-color: #333333;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n\n        #podcasts {\n            padding: 50px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        #podcasts h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item {\n            background-color: #282828;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-item img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-info {\n            padding: 20px;\n            flex-grow: 1;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-info h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-info p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n            color: #ccc;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-info .listen-now {\n            display: inline-block;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-info .listen-now:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        #about {\n            background-color: #222;\n            padding: 50px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        #about h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        #about p {\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            color: #ddd;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--footer-color);\n            color: #bbb;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n\n        footer a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n\n        .scrollToTop {\n            position: fixed;\n            bottom: 20px;\n            right: 30px;\n            z-index: 99;\n            border: none;\n            outline: none;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            cursor: pointer;\n            padding: 15px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            font-size: 18px;\n            opacity: 0.8;\n            transition: opacity 0.4s, background-color 0.4s;\n            display: none;\n        }\n\n        .scrollToTop:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            opacity: 1;\n        }\n\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>EchoSphere Network</h1>\n            <p>Hear the world. Your daily dose of captivating stories and insightful discussions.</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"podcasts\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Featured Podcasts</h2>\n            <div class=\"podcast-grid\">\n                <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x200/ff4500/ffffff?text=Cosmic+Chronicles\" alt=\"Cosmic Chronicles Podcast Cover\">\n                    <div class=\"podcast-info\">\n                        <div>\n                            <h3>Cosmic Chronicles</h3>\n                            <p>Journey through the vastness of space, exploring the latest discoveries and the mysteries of the universe.</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <a href=\"#\" class=\"listen-now\">Listen Now</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x200/ff7f50/ffffff?text=Tech+Talks+Today\" alt=\"Tech Talks Today Podcast Cover\">\n                    <div class=\"podcast-info\">\n                        <div>\n                            <h3>Tech Talks Today</h3>\n                            <p>The pulse of innovation. Deep dives into AI, cybersecurity, and the future of technology.</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <a href=\"#\" class=\"listen-now\">Listen Now</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x200/ff4500/ffffff?text=History+Uncovered\" alt=\"History Uncovered Podcast Cover\">\n                    <div class=\"podcast-info\">\n                        <div>\n                            <h3>History Uncovered</h3>\n                            <p>Unearthing forgotten tales and hidden narratives that shaped our world.</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <a href=\"#\" class=\"listen-now\">Listen Now</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x200/ff7f50/ffffff?text=Mindful+Moments\" alt=\"Mindful Moments Podcast Cover\">\n                    <div class=\"podcast-info\">\n                        <div>\n                            <h3>Mindful Moments</h3>\n                            <p>Find peace and clarity with guided meditations and discussions on well-being.</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <a href=\"#\" class=\"listen-now\">Listen Now</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About EchoSphere</h2>\n            <p>\n                EchoSphere Network is dedicated to bringing you high-quality audio content across a diverse range of topics. From the furthest reaches of space to the intricacies of human history and the cutting edge of technology, we aim to inform, entertain, and inspire. Our passionate creators are committed to crafting compelling narratives and thought-provoking conversations that resonate with listeners worldwide.\n            </p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 EchoSphere Network. All rights reserved.</p>\n            <p>Discover more of our shows on <a href=\"#\">our platform</a>.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <button onclick=\"topFunction()\" id=\"scrollToTopBtn\" title=\"Go to top\">^</button>\n\n    <script>\n        let mybutton = document.getElementById(\"scrollToTopBtn\");\n\n        window.onscroll = function() {scrollFunction()};\n\n        function scrollFunction() {\n            if (document.body.scrollTop > 20 || document.documentElement.scrollTop > 20) {\n                mybutton.style.display = \"block\";\n            } else {\n                mybutton.style.display = \"none\";\n            }\n        }\n\n        function topFunction() {\n            document.body.scrollTop = 0;\n            document.documentElement.scrollTop = 0;\n        }\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}